title: Around the NFC in 48 minutes!
itunes:title: Around the NFC in 48 minutes!
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling, & Gregg Rosenthal – go around the NFC breaking down the state of every team following the 2017 NFL Draft, and discuss which division improved the most through the draft.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
